    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 RemotePlay Together 最多可与 4 名玩家联机玩 CTHULOOT，而且只需一份游戏副本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/fe538e6daa05e3bc581fc875abbd67e7.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/fe538e6daa05e3bc581fc875abbd67e7.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>旧日支配者正在召唤！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召集好友组建一支半吊子的抢夺者队伍，寻找旧日支配者遗失的神器吧。在这期间千万小心不要唤醒它们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/96fbff71c148e983360481231112f4a9.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/96fbff71c148e983360481231112f4a9.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>和好友同乐的多人合作游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索存在与现实和疯狂之间的神秘领域，并沿途收集各种疯狂的战利品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/c235af52eaa220693ef816ec23b767f5.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/c235af52eaa220693ef816ec23b767f5.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>找到并收集古代神器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用收集到的宝藏的力量，帮助莫加兹汗领主重获其在旧日支配者中应有的地位。利用他的超自然怀表物品来获得新技能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/1bb0097151a562da9f76e44bf8050fd8.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/1bb0097151a562da9f76e44bf8050fd8.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在一切结束之时，你们的友谊还会如同当初吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以突出表现展示身为抢夺者的才华，如果不想给团队拖后腿的话，那就不要错过沿途的任何东西喔！</p>",
